    <s:String x:Key="Settings_Tab_Delays">Text Transfer Delays</s:String>
    <s:String x:Key="Settings_TimingGroup">Text Timing Settings</s:String>
    <s:String x:Key="Settings_TimingHint">These delays are tuned to match Google Translate's behavior. Keep values roughly between 50 and 5000 milliseconds.</s:String>
    <s:String x:Key="Settings_ProcessDelay">Text processing delay</s:String>
    <s:String x:Key="Settings_Milliseconds">ms</s:String>
    <s:String x:Key="Settings_ProcessDelayHint">Time between receiving speech from Google Translate and starting processing. Suggested: 300–500</s:String>
    <s:String x:Key="Settings_WordDelay">Word-by-word delay</s:String>
    <s:String x:Key="Settings_WordDelayHint">Time between typing each word into the target app. Suggested: 250–400</s:String>
    <s:String x:Key="Settings_StartDelay">Transfer start delay</s:String>
    <s:String x:Key="Settings_StartDelayHint">Wait time after the first recognition before auto-transfer begins. Suggested: 1500–2500</s:String>
    <s:String x:Key="Settings_InactivityDelay">Pause before microphone reset</s:String>
    <s:String x:Key="Settings_InactivityDelayHint">Silence duration before the microphone auto-resets. Suggested: 2500–5000</s:String>
    <s:String x:Key="Settings_TimingFooter">These delays are tuned to work correctly with Google Translate. If text is typed late or incompletely, increase the word-by-word delay first.</s:String>
    <s:String x:Key="Settings_Tab_GoogleTranslate">Google Translate Settings</s:String>
    <s:String x:Key="Settings_SelectorsGroup">Google Translate Web Selectors</s:String>
    <s:String x:Key="Settings_SelectorsHint">These values identify the microphone button and text box on the Google Translate page. If Google changes its design, just update these values.</s:String>
